Baron '''Lutwill''' was a self-appointed petty lord of a region southeast of the [[Starspire Mountains]] during the [[Tethyrian Interregnum]].
{{Quote|[[Zazesspur]] will reward me mightily when I send them your head preserved in [[vinegar]].|Baron Lutwill to [[Zaranda Star]] (She argued that it would be better preserved in [[brandy]].)}}
